<p class="ql-align-center">（曾鸣）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200915/512bc578d42d4299b4eb54edc36525aa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（胡树真）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200915/b215d2519f6d4bcaa179931d44b86ea9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（陈小雨）</p>